snippet.textDisplay: This is the Highlight of this game, it's amazing how it builds up just like the fight with the big baddie, King K Rool.  It keeps the tension high while he throws his crown, jumps up and down, and has cannonballs fall on you, this song is etched into my brain since I was a kid.
